"{\"uid\": \"thenews.com.pk-latest-1216279-cody-simpson-celebrates-emma-mckeons-olympic-journey\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Cody Simpson has honored his girlfriend, Olympic swimmer Emma McKeon, with a heartfelt tribute as she competes in Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 120, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 12, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cody_Simpson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cody Simpson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cody_Simpson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cody_Simpson\"}, {\"begin\": 57, \"end\": 68, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_McKeon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emma McKeon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_McKeon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_McKeon\"}, {\"begin\": 114, \"end\": 119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998256463566, \"rank\": 1.7435113391154497e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Saturday, Simpson shared a photo on social media of himself wearing a T-shirt that celebrated McKeon's achievements.\", \"from\": 122, \"to\": 241, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The shirt, featuring multiple images of McKeon in the pool and showcasing her Olympic medals, was adorned with the word \\\"Emma\\\" and green and gold heart emojis.\", \"from\": 243, \"to\": 402, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 364, \"end\": 368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Swan\", \"score\": 0.9844620119311729, \"rank\": 0.013610197766409352, \"text\": \"Emma\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Swan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Swan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old, who narrowly missed qualifying for the Olympics himself, has been actively supporting her during her quest for gold.\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 537, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She is celebrated as Australia's most successful Olympian, and Simpson's tribute highlights his pride in her remarkable career.\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 666, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 560, \"end\": 569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9817083332254668, \"rank\": 0.014293053407802694, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 588, \"end\": 596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9998311914773962, \"rank\": 0.00016883649767562186, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Emma McKeon has revealed her intention to retire following the conclusion of the Paris Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 769, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 668, \"end\": 679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_McKeon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emma McKeon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_McKeon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_McKeon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The announcement comes as McKeon, already celebrated as Australia's most successful Olympian, secured her sixth gold medal with a victory in the 4x100m freestyle relay.\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 939, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 827, \"end\": 836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9817083332254668, \"rank\": 0.014293053407802694, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 855, \"end\": 863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9998311914773962, \"rank\": 0.00016883649767562186, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This win brings her total to 12 Olympic medals since 2016, surpassing the legendary Ian Thorpe's count of five golds.\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 1058, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1025, \"end\": 1035, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ian_Thorpe\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ian Thorpe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ian_Thorpe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ian_Thorpe\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2025.\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1077, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The News International, All Rights Reserved\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1121, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1078, \"end\": 1100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_News_International\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The News International\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_News_International\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_News_International\"}]}]}"